      "The Eiffel Tower is in Paris.",
      "The Great Wall of China is in China.",
      "The Pacific is an ocean.",
      "Photosynthesis happens in plants.",
      "DNA carries genetic information.",
      "The speed of light is approximately 299792 km/s.",
      "Shakespeare wrote Hamlet.",
      "The Mona Lisa was painted by Leonardo da Vinci.",
      "Beethoven was a composer.",
      "Mozart was a composer.",
      "The Earth orbits the Sun.",
      "The Moon orbits the Earth.",
      "Jupiter is the largest planet in our solar system.",
      "The Amazon is a rainforest.",
      "Penguins live in Antarctica.",
      "Lions are carnivores.",
      "Humans have 23 pairs of chromosomes.",
      "Oxygen is necessary for human respiration.",
      "Gold is a chemical element.",
      "The Statue of Liberty is in New York.",
      "Big Ben is in London.",
      "The Colosseum is in Rome.",
      "The Pyramids of Giza are in Egypt.",
